#

Cilantro Lime Grilled Chicken Tacos

$15
350 kcal
Difficulty: 40%

Allergens:

None

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeHigh-Protein

Tags:

MexicanGrilledTacos

Description

Zesty grilled chicken wrapped in soft corn tortillas, topped with fresh pico de gallo and creamy avocado.

Ingredients

  • Boneless Chicken Thighs: 1 lb
  • Olive Oil: 2 tbsp
  • Lime Juice: 2 tbsp
  • Cilantro: 1/4 cup, chopped
  • Garlic: 2 cloves, minced
  • Corn Tortillas: 8
  • Pico de Gallo: 1 cup
  • Avocado: 1, sliced
  • Salt and Pepper: to taste
